          -------------------------------------------------------------
          WELCOME TO THE WORLD OF THE DUPLICATOR TOOLKIT
          -------------------------------------------------------------
          Thank you for purchasing this program!  THE DUPLICATOR TOOLKIT
          quickly and reliably makes copies of diskettes.  The program
          can copy 360K, 720K, 1.2M or 1.44M diskettes on PC, XT, AT or
          PS/2 machines.  Generally, THE DUPLICATOR uses the hard disk
          to "buffer" the master diskette data.

          We continually review user input for updates.  If you have any
          comments, suggestions, or an unusual application, please drop
          us a line.

          -------------------------------------------------------------
          WHAT THIS DOCUMENT CONTAINS
          -------------------------------------------------------------
          This document contains information about Version 3.0 of THE
          DUPLICATOR TOOLKIT.  The information contained in this
          document is more up to date than that in the THE DUPLICATOR
          TOOLKIT Users Manual.  Consequently, where information in the
          manual conflicts with information in this document, this
          document should be assumed to contain the correct information.

